name: Tut-Ank's 3333th Birthday Bash
description:
"Hey Hoodie-Bird, you are late to the party, but you can still get there. Let the balloons guide your way. but careful, they say the cacti in this area become alive at night..."

Visit the good old Tutankhamun, it's his 3333th birthday today.

Jump with Space, avoid the Cacti, join the party.
